# ğŸ  rental_price_challenge

This is my **first Machine Learning project with a user interface (UI)**.  
It predicts rental prices for houses based on simple input features like size, number of rooms, and location. The UI was built using [Gradio](https://gradio.app/) to make it easy for anyone to test the model.

